OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775775781
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer explains why Iran will
OL,4,Cdefine his government
OL,6,FMy Talking Politics podcast
OL,7,Fconversation with Keir Starmer ranged
OL,8,Ffrom his critical reaction to Trump's
OL,9,Finflammatory Truth Social posts all
OL,10,Fthe way through to reshaping defence
OL,11,Ffor this new age of drone wars and his
OL,12,Fzeal to forge new, closer
OL,13,Frelationships with the EU and other
OL,14,FEuropean countries.
OL,16,FFor what it's worth, I found him more
OL,17,Fanimated and engaged than I have seen
OL,18,Fhim for some time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
