OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775775781
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer explains why Iran will
OL,4,Cdefine his government
OL,6,FIf you think he has a future after
OL,7,Fwhat are expected to be disastrous
OL,8,Flocal and national elections for
OL,9,FLabour in May, and diminishing numbers
OL,10,Fof his MPs are plotting to
OL,11,Fdefenestrate him, you should listen to
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FTwo of his remarks stood out to me.
OL,15,FFirst was his belief that Trump's Iran
OL,16,Fwar will define his time in office, as
OL,17,Fmuch as the 2007/8 global financial
OL,18,Fcrisis did for Gordon Brown and Covid
OL,19,Fdid for Boris Johnson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
