FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1775775781
OL,3,CPeston: Starmer explains why Iran will
OL,4,Cdefine his government
OL,6,FStarmer pledged that, unlike his
OL,7,Fpredecessors, he would not waste this
OL,8,Fcrisis and would use it to push
OL,9,Fthrough fundamental reforms, whose
OL,10,Fmain aim would be to lift up the
OL,11,Fliving standards of those left behind
OL,12,Fover the past 20 years.
OL,14,FListen to the podcast to decide
OL,15,Fwhether his ambitious rhetoric is
OL,16,Funderpinned by credible plans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
