OL,3,CPeston: Starmer explains why Iran will
OL,4,Cdefine his government
OL,6,FI fear he does not yet fully recognise
OL,7,Fthe inevitable trade-offs between
OL,8,Fgrowth and equity, in a winner-takes-
OL,9,Fall AI world. But he is certainly on a
OL,10,Fjourney, as they say.
OL,12,FSecond, and more trivially, he
OL,13,Frevealed that he is part of assorted
OL,14,FWhatsApp groups with world leaders,
OL,15,Ffor a variety of shared projects.
OL,17,FThe greatest proponent of the
OL,18,FWhatsApping culture in his peer group
OL,19,Fis Finland's president, Alex Stubb.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
